{"tid":2514475,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"湯家驊：傳媒「反送中」描述是謊言","createTime":"2021-05-03T09:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T09:46:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f79b85b6739f6023db86631e97f5c17c8a8dfb7a","tid":2514475,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:34:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210503/6S3W7H4LO5AZHDJBX2CKSXH7MI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210503%2F6S3W7H4LO5AZHDJBX2CKSXH7MI%2F&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOARUsGYs0X8VP9vM6mjQjJM%3D&h=4f363cc4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210503%2F6S3W7H4LO5AZHDJBX2CKSXH7MI%2F&h=fef50bb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210503/6S3W7H4LO5AZHDJBX2CKSXH7MI/</a><br />\n<br />\n湯家驊：傳媒「反送中」描述是謊言<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】特首林鄭月娥日前接受內地《瞭望》新聞周刊專訪時指，香港特區仍有大量制度有待完善，例如教育、傳媒和公務員培訓與管理等，行政會議成員湯家驊昨於港台英文節目《給香港的信》，不點名批評《蘋果日報》以「反送中」描述由修訂《逃犯條例》所引起一連串的社會運動，指海外媒體及外國政府寧願相信「謊言」，共同煽動社區的憤怒和仇恨，令香港「瀕臨完全瓦解的邊緣」（the brink of total disintegration）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/G7ovBNaPvUBx8OLuOyWjQnmn-QU=/510x428/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FAJ62UXAVZBRHGJE43RRBSC5CU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FG7ovBNaPvUBx8OLuOyWjQnmn-QU%3D%2F510x428%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFAJ62UXAVZBRHGJE43RRBSC5CU.jpg&h=aa9cff15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■湯家驊昨在節目中指外國政府相信「謊言」，令香港瀕臨瓦解邊緣。港台圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n促政府糾正「錯誤訊息」<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊在《給香港的信》節目中指，一國兩制的最大挑戰是「謊言和誤導」，指有人策劃摧毀一國兩制，故意說謊，令社區出現很多謊言和誤導。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊以單程證配額為例，指有人仍堅信其是用以搶劫（robbing）港人的社會福利；又指部份具法律背景的政客或立法者甚至公開表態相信「反觀點」。<br />\n<br />\n湯續指，前年因修訂《逃。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n湯認為，要避免「謊言和誤導。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n不過，湯家驊認為政府並非無事可做，他建議政府建立公眾溝通和諮詢的渠道。。。。。"},{"pid":"fc86e9ac784f1cc91a5ac05112d0485033a96834","tid":2514475,"uid":42762,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:41:36.000Z","msg":"湯家驊最大的挑戰是「淚灑雪廠街」"},{"pid":"2a351342f584f5e103ad479ce1c918edb1794a37","tid":2514475,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fc86e9ac784f1cc91a5ac05112d0485033a96834","tid":2514475,"uid":42762,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:41:36.000Z","msg":"湯家驊最大的挑戰是「淚灑雪廠街」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:44:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/23/121229_c9b288dc140648cb5d16fa5245c61e2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F23%2F121229_c9b288dc140648cb5d16fa5245c61e2e.jpg&h=82766cb3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1deb2c16012aaf4c3f373dd5e5ebf997ae931997","tid":2514475,"uid":19908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:45:12.000Z","msg":"重推逃犯條例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d27c0939d08b5fe17e59247b0f9fe25fc9aa3fd","tid":2514475,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:46:20.000Z","msg":"反送中是謊言？即係送中是事實啦。"}]}